00:26:18.409 --> 00:26:24.940
The Fed is taking the slack for the retirees
and people leaving the labor force.

00:26:24.940 --> 00:26:26.059
This is all they're doing.

00:26:26.059 --> 00:26:27.980
They're trying to offset this.

00:26:27.980 --> 00:26:33.460
Now, whether they are cognisant of doing this
or not, this is essentially what they're doing.

00:26:33.460 --> 00:26:36.539
It's so fascinating, and it makes total sense
to me.

00:26:36.539 --> 00:26:42.659
What I love about demographics is you can
essentially extrapolate forward the demographics

00:26:42.659 --> 00:26:45.749
of a nation because it's baked in the cake.

00:26:45.749 --> 00:26:49.470
When those people are born, you kind of know
when they're going to die, roughly what they're

00:26:49.470 --> 00:26:52.639
going to do, and how they're going operate
within the economy.

